      <title>博尔索纳罗在里约集会上赞扬马斯克，因为他的法律问题日益严重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/jair-bolsonaro-praises-elon-musk-at-brazil-rally-amid-police-probes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前总统雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗称赞埃隆·马斯克是言论自由的倡导者，这是他在法律麻烦不断增加之际发起反对该国最高法院的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/jair-bolsonaro-praises-elon-musk-at-brazil-rally-amid-police-probes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 16:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>审判正在进行中，特朗普只剩下 680 万美元的法律费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trump-has-only-6-8-million-for-legal-fees-with-trial-underway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[竞选财务文件显示，唐纳德·特朗普3月份在法律费用上花费了490万美元，而他用来资助律师的账户中只剩下680万美元，随着审判费用的增加，他将面临现金短缺的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trump-has-only-6-8-million-for-legal-fees-with-trial-underway</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 15:43:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着现金索赔立法者退出，苏纳克的保守党受到新的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/sunak-s-tories-dealt-a-fresh-blow-as-cash-claims-lawmaker-quits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名面临不当行为指控的保守党议员表示，他将在下次选举中辞去议员职务，导致总理里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 难以阻止丑闻席卷其政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/sunak-s-tories-dealt-a-fresh-blow-as-cash-claims-lawmaker-quits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 15:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称美国的援助为乌克兰提供了重新夺回主动权的手段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ukraine-war-zelenskiy-says-aid-gives-ukraine-the-means-to-retake-initiative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统泽连斯基表示，美国的新支持使乌克兰有可能在对抗俄罗斯入侵的斗争中重新掌握主动权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ukraine-war-zelenskiy-says-aid-gives-ukraine-the-means-to-retake-initiative</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 13:49:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗最高领袖：袭击以色列的导弹数量“小问题”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/iran-s-supreme-leader-number-of-missiles-that-hit-israel-trivial-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领导人赞扬了该国一周前对以色列的报复性打击，尽管他认为德黑兰打击目标的成功率低是一件微不足道的事情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/iran-s-supreme-leader-number-of-missiles-that-hit-israel-trivial-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔在诺博亚关键测试中投票决定引渡黑手党头目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecuador-votes-on-extradition-for-mafia-bosses-in-key-test-for-noboa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔举行公投，允许将黑手党头目引渡到美国监狱，这是对总统丹尼尔·诺博亚受欢迎程度的首次严峻考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecuador-votes-on-extradition-for-mafia-bosses-in-key-test-for-noboa</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:08:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织面临反对新兴市场债务重做蓝图的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界金融领导人正在推动彻底改革主权债务重组体系，该体系使贫穷国家被排除在资本市场之外，因为中国作为关键参与者的出现颠覆了传统谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅希望重新夺回主动权，泽伦斯基欢呼美国的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局对美国众议院批准超过 600 亿美元的援助感到欢欣鼓舞，不过焦点已转移到援助能以多快的速度到达前线，以及该计划将如何改变基辅在对抗俄罗斯入侵的斗争中的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 11:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡谴责美国制裁陆军的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/netanyahu-condemns-reported-us-plan-to-blacklist-military-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡谴责了据报道的美国计划对约旦河西岸侵犯人权行为实施制裁的极端正统派军队营，此举可能会加剧以色列针对加沙哈马斯战争的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/netanyahu-condemns-reported-us-plan-to-blacklist-military-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 09:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对加沙南部城市拉法的袭击造成 22 人死亡，其中大部分是儿童</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-21/israeli-strikes-on-southern-gaza-city-of-rafah-kill-13-mostly-children-as-us-advances-aid-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带拉法（美联社）卫生官员周日表示，以色列对加沙南部城市拉法的袭击一夜之间造成 22 人死亡，其中包括 18 名儿童，而美国正准备批准向其亲密盟友以色列提供数十亿美元的额外军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-21/israeli-strikes-on-southern-gaza-city-of-rafah-kill-13-mostly-children-as-us-advances-aid-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 07:19:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
